cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with image re-ranking, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Privileged Information (PI) and the integration of global and local features suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of embeddings and the on-the-fly re-ranking suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
